1. Create your deploy folder ready with all the files and requirements.txt files.
2. Create your EC2 instance and security group.
3. Add the security group to your instance.
4. SSH into your EC2 instance.(use connect option in your ec2 instance)
    ssh -i "key_pair_01.pem" ubuntu@ec2-13-126-115-198.ap-south-1.compute.amazonaws.com
5. Check if everything is working fine.Then logout using logout command.
6. Now we need to add the deploy_folder to the instance using scp command.
    scp -i -r "your_key_pair.pem" deploy_folder ubuntu@your_ip.ap-south-1.compute.amazonaws.com:~/
7. again connect to instance and run these below scripts :
    1. sudo apt update
    2. sudo apt upgrade
    3. sudo apt install python3
    4. sudo apt install python3-pip
    5. sudo apt install python3-venv
8. Create your virtual environment and activate it.
    1. python3 -m venv venv
    2. source venv/bin/activate
9. Install your dependencies.
    1. pip install -r requirements.txt
10. Run your app.
    1. streamlit run app.py
    2. python app.py
11. Test your app.
